headline: The race to embrace stablecoins heats up on Wall Street
summary: Wall Street isn't just celebrating the debut of a major stablecoin issuer as Circle's stock soared Thursday. It's also considering how it can compete against Circle in the future.

headline: JPMorgan Bets on Branches in Digital Age: A Smart Growth Move?
summary: JPM is doubling down on brick-and-mortar branches, blending in-person banking with digital tools to unlock cross-selling opportunities and grow revenues.
